        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/condi-weaver/">&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fast paced, high APM, press everything off cooldown build rotating between &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5492&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Fire Attunement and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;5495&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Earth Attunement for maximum burning and bleeding damage.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Condition Weaver relies on rotating quickly through two elements in order to have high uptime on both &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2180&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Weaver&#x27;s Prowess and &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2131&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Elements of Rage, increasing damage done and condition duration.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build is also primarily ranged, accounting for ~93% of it&#x27;s damage. Small tweaks can be made to bring this number up to ~98%, and will be addressed under advanced tips.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
